 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Allows use of up to three Weaponskills without combo requirements. Grants Fugetsu on use of Gekko and Fuka on use of Kasha. Excludes laijutsu and Ogi Namikiri. Grants Tendo. 20s duration, 55s CD.&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
