&lt;/div>
&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Meditate&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Channeled Kenki and Meditation stack generation for 15s. Initial cast on the GCD. +10 Kenki (Max 50) and +1 Meditation stack (Max 3) per tick. Cancelled upon movement or action. Can only be used in combat. 60s CD.&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
